title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_hall" target="_blank">conference</a> opens on May 6Other speakers include <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/City_council" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/City_council" target="_blank">city council</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leadership" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leadership" target="_blank">leader</a> Gordon Matheson <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Professor" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Professor" target="_blank">Professor</a> Sir Jim McDonald Principal and ViceChancellor of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Strathclyde" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Strathclyde" target="_blank">Strathclyde University</a> Benj Sykes head of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asset_management" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asset_management" target="_blank">asset management</a> at <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/DONG_Energy" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/DONG_Energy" target="_blank">DONG Energy</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wind_power" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wind_power" target="_blank">Wind Power</a> and Ian Marchant former <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_executive_officer" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_executive_officer" target="_blank">chief executive</a> of SSEThe full <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_hall" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_hall" target="_blank">conference</a> programme is online at wwwallenergycouk as both an interactive <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electrical_grid" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electrical_grid" target="_blank">grid</a> which leads to biographical details of each speaker and as a quick and easy to use pdf of the whole programmeAdmission to the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Men%27s_major_golf_championships" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Men%27s_major_golf_championships" target="_blank">major</a> <a href="http://dbpedi